&gt; The queen buzzed in the air, floating as she looked carefully at
&gt; Talon, Straightshot and Tuscon for a long moment before she laughed!
&gt; &quot;You have nothing to offer me that I cannot take for myself. I have no
&gt; fear of you Cybertronians.&quot; Her words cold and arrogant, dripping with
&gt; scorn.
&gt;
&gt; She turned to look at small pod that housed Rodimus, her humor still
&gt; evident. With a quick slash of one of her bladed forelegs she cut
&gt; through part of the webbed adhesive that was holding the pod in place
&gt; and the pod began to sink toward the ground.
&gt;
&gt; &quot;Take him!&quot; she said derisively, &quot;He has already given me all that I
&gt; need to know.&quot; She floated higher into the air as she looked at the
&gt; group, the beat of her wings causing a cool breeze to stir around the
&gt; chamber.
&gt;
&gt; &quot;For it seems we have others to take his place.&quot; The queen&#39;s voice was
&gt; almost hungry as she spoke. Meanwhile, from the same direction that
&gt; Tuscon and his group had entered insectile soldiers entered, evidently
&gt; the last ones they had encountered from the bruises and dents on a
&gt; few. This time they were carrying what appeared to Scourge at first,
&gt; or at least two of him, although they were slightly lighter in color -
&gt; They were Sweeps, the drone minions of the implacable hunter!
&gt;
&gt; She laughs, &quot;My children will feed well, and learn still more.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; From a few of the hundreds of dark openings a few insect like
&gt; creatures came out. These looked somewhat different than the ones the
&gt; group has seen before. Looking like a cross between a spider and a
&gt; mantis, they had scorpion no tail cannon like the others, instead they
&gt; had positioned on their bodies cannon mounts and rocket launchers,
&gt; although they did have the same mantis legs and blades. However the
&gt; most striking features was their color. Instead of the darker colors
&gt; the others have been, these were yellow and orange and red - Rodimus&#39;
&gt; colors!
&gt;
&gt; &quot;Go my would be guardians.&quot; the queen said mockingly, &quot;Leave now
&gt; before my children grow too hungry too soon!&quot; More children began to
&gt; be seen coming from the caves as she spoke, although for the moment
&gt; none of them were approaching the group, but were instead lifting
&gt; their heads upwards as if sniffing the air.
